//
// File: zannastudio/src/commands/main_command_dispatcher.zia
// Purpose: Route menu, toolbar, shortcut, palette, explorer, and overlay work
//          through shared Studio command workflows.
// Key invariants:
//   - Canceled/rejected commands do not mutate dependent controller state.
//   - Workspace changes keep indexing and terminal context synchronized.
//   - Scene selection shortcuts never escape hierarchy/viewport focus, while
//     explicit palette selections remain executable after focus moves.
// Ownership/Lifetime: Stateless dispatcher borrowing one CommandContext.
// Links: zannastudio/src/commands/command_context.zia,
//        zannastudio/src/main.zia
//
//===----------------------------------------------------------------------===//

